{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "6.840", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "6.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.560", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.720", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.360", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr von Stetten wird als gro\u00dfer Erbe und potenziell Betroffener offenbar sehr nerv\u00f6s;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.040", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber wir beraten heute ja \u00fcber einen Antrag der Fraktion Die Linke aus der letzten Legislatur. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.320", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist in der Tat Wort f\u00fcr Wort der gleiche Antrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.760", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich h\u00e4tte mir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.720", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ehrlich gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.600", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der neuen Legislatur ein bisschen mehr Kreativit\u00e4t gew\u00fcnscht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.120", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zumal es neuere Erkenntnisse gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich dachte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.480", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihnen in der letzten Debatte ein paar Punkte mit auf den Weg gegeben zu haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.720", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.960", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die 5-Prozent-Forderung der Linken ist haneb\u00fcchen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.640", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da sie den Milliard\u00e4r genauso stellt wie den dreifachen Million\u00e4r."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.480", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zudem sieht sie f\u00fcr den Fall, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.920", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Hochverm\u00f6gende ins Ausland verschwinden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.480", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "keine globale Steuerpflicht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.120", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nach der der deutsche Milliard\u00e4r auch dann steuerpflichtig wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.320", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn er beispielsweise auf Barbados wohnt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gut gemeint ist nicht immer gut gemacht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.240", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "werte Kolleginnen und Kollegen der Linken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.880", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie es besser geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.040", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zeigt der Deutsche Gewerkschaftsbund, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.400", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der ganz im Sinne der Besteuerung der Leistungsf\u00e4higkeit eine progressive Verm\u00f6gensteuer vorschl\u00e4gt: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.200", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der dreifache Million\u00e4r zahlt 1\u00a0Prozent, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Milliard\u00e4r 2\u00a0Prozent. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.680", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das nenne ich progressiv, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "86.560", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist gerecht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "86.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das ist auch ein Novum. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "93.440", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Sozialdemokraten werden uns das DGB-Modell sehr genau ansehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "93.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verm\u00f6gensungleichheit ist nicht nur in Deutschland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.040", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch in Europa erschreckend hoch; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.360", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist unstrittig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.080", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Trend besch\u00e4digt nicht nur unseren Staat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unsere Gesellschaft und unsere Demokratie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.760", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern er ist auch \u00f6konomisch sch\u00e4dlich. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In kaum einem anderen Land\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.880", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das wurde hier schon gesagt\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.120", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist der Beitrag des Verm\u00f6gens zum Steueraufkommen geringer als in Deutschland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.160", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich pers\u00f6nlich habe keinerlei Probleme mit einer sofortigen Wiederbelebung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.800", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Partei lehnt die Verm\u00f6gensteuer auch nicht ab. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.440", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Gegenteil ist der Fall: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.520", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verm\u00f6gensteuer ist fester Bestandteil unseres Grundsatzprogramms. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.760", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist offensichtlich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir aufgrund der Verm\u00f6gensungleichheit eine fundierte Besteuerung von Verm\u00f6gen in Deutschland brauchen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.560", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob dies mit einer Verm\u00f6gensteuer oder mit einer echten Erbschaftsteuer geschehen soll, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.160", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "pr\u00fcfen wir aktuell in einer Kommission beim SPD-Parteivorstand."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.720", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr uns ist klar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.680", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir bei einer Wiedererhebung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer nach dem Prinzip \u201eGr\u00fcndlichkeit geht vor Schnelligkeit\u201c vorgehen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.720", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daher werden wir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.880", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bevor wir zu einem abschlie\u00dfenden Ergebnis kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.760", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das Urteil des Bundesverfassungsgerichts zur Grundsteuer abwarten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.720", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die m\u00fcndliche Verhandlung hat vor zwei Tagen stattgefunden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.720", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Rahmen dieser Grundsteuerreform wird es zu einer marktn\u00e4heren Bewertung von Grundst\u00fccken kommen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das ist entscheidend f\u00fcr die Auferstehung der Verm\u00f6gensteuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klar ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.320", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in dieser Frage gro\u00dfe Gemeinsamkeiten mit den Linken und den Gr\u00fcnen haben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Klar ist aber auch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.080", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass eine Verm\u00f6gensteuer nur in dieser Konstellation wirksam umgesetzt werden kann."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An dieser Stelle ist es mir auch wichtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.000", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu betonen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.880", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Grundgesetz hat kein Problem mit der Verm\u00f6gensteuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.480", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Gegenteil. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.040", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum sonst steht die Verm\u00f6gensteuer im Grundgesetz? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Waren die M\u00fctter und V\u00e4ter des Grundgesetzes Verfassungsfeinde? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.920", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie konnte Deutschland in der Nachkriegszeit mit einer Verm\u00f6gensteuer und einer Lastenausgleichsabgabe ein Wirtschaftswunder erleben?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "240.680", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind Fragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "240.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "242.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die sich die Gegner der Verm\u00f6gensteuer\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "242.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.920", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch Herr von Stetten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.240", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einmal stellen sollten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.760", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit es alle richtig verstehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.080", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sage ich es deutlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.480", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit es in Deutschland gerechter zugeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.880", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen wir eine h\u00f6here Besteuerung von H\u00f6chstverm\u00f6genden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.880", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und nat\u00fcrlich brauchen wir auch verm\u00f6gensbezogene Steuern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.000", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die ihrem Namen gerecht werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.200", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verm\u00f6gensteuer ist in dieser Diskussion nat\u00fcrlich nicht alternativlos. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "276.160", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Alternativlosigkeit gibt es nur im Neoliberalismus oder in einer marktgerechten Demokratie. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "276.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "278.960", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer die Verm\u00f6gensteuer nicht will, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "278.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "287.080", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss an h\u00f6here Steuers\u00e4tze f\u00fcr gro\u00dfe Einkommen denken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "287.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "292.280", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00f6glich w\u00e4re zum Beispiel ein h\u00f6herer Spitzensteuersatz oder eine weitere Reform der Erbschaftsteuer."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "292.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.480", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die letzte Reform der Erbschaftsteuer wird die erforderliche Umverteilung auf jeden Fall nicht bringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.840", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin mir sicher, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "307.400", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die sozialstaatlichen Mahnungen aus dem Jahr\u00a02014 von den Verfassungsrichtern vermutlich erneuert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "307.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "308.760", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden es sehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "308.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.240", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber klar ist: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "310.240", 
   "children": [], 
